&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://d33wubrfki0l68.cloudfront.net/c38c7334cc3f23585738e4033284fddcaf03d5e/2e17c/images/hugo-logo-wide.svg&#34;/&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;
            &lt;h4&gt;Hugo logo&lt;/h4&gt;
